  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Given validator requests assignment at the start of the epoch, in the case of a reorg back to the start of the epoch that cause validator assignments to change, validators currently have no way of knowing such reorg event and will still request based on the \"old\" assignment\r\nOpening this issue for discussion and mitigation steps \r\n\r\nDesign doc: https://hackmd.io/KWBj0PCDQUuPKpLQnIiZbw?both",
